verses.verse: Iron, Migdal El, Horem, Beth Anath, and Beth Shemesh: nineteen cities with their villages.
This was the inheritance of the tribe of the children of Naphtali according to their families, the cities and their villages.
(The Land of Dan) (Josh. 19:40-48; Judg. 1:34-36) The seventh lot came out for the tribe of the children of Dan according to their families.
And the territory of their inheritance was Zorah, (Josh. 15:33) Eshtaol, Ir Shemesh,
Me Jarkon, and Rakkon, with the region near Joppa.
